          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "郭太师在朝中势力皆大"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "似这等犯王法儿全然不怕"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "爹爹不必怒气发，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孩儿言来听根芽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怒恼了你孩儿将他来杀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在府门与郭荣百般叫骂"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "小奴才说此话胆比天大，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "打死人还说是不犯王法！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在府门与郭荣百般叫骂"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿是好汉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿是好汉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "是好汉随老父参王见驾，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "少刻间见万岁，谁是谁非，儿要启奏皇家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣，姚期见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚皇兄你可知罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣知罪，不知罪犯何条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有你三子姚刚，骑马游街，将郭老太师打死。你还言无罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "郭老太师也有一行大罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罪犯何条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在府门以外私立三尺禁地，文官下轿，武官离鞍。万岁可曾降旨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……孤王有言在先，未曾降旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁无旨，斩者无亏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个“斩者无亏”！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绑坏了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，殿角下绑的何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三子姚刚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，快快松绑，不要绑坏孤的少爱卿！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（太监甲松绑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁不之恩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是孤王不斩与你，是孤先前许下“姚不反汉，汉不斩姚”。赐你三千人马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去到湖北枉子城，保定金固牛庄。你父子午门一别，下殿去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期、姚刚",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚刚 （三笑） 哈哈，哈哈，哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "万岁爷赦了姚霸林，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "好似枯木又逢春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "开言叫声姚霸林："
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "儿不要提刀乱杀人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿来看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手拉姣儿下龙廷"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番湖北儿要改性情"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为父的年迈苍苍白如银，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "姚刚，我的儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "好一似瓦上霜、风前灯，能过几春？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "爹爹落泪儿悲伤，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "点点珠泪洒胸膛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在朝为官有什么好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一点不到有损伤！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "告职回乡乐安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "回府去拜上老萱堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚刚",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，我父，爹爹吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姚刚下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚刚，霸林，哎吓我的儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "金殿去了姚霸林，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "父子们相逢万不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "告职回乡乐安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启见万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转过金阶梧桐树"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，姚皇兄为何去而复返？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启万岁：臣要告职归林。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇兄告职，寡人怎样舍得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要臣在朝伴驾，依臣一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁戒酒百日，老臣方能在朝伴驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只要皇兄在朝，慢说戒酒百日，就是周年半岁，又待何妨？内侍，将姚皇兄扶"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（太监甲扶姚期。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "姚皇兄休得要告职还乡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "龙书案听寡人细说端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫寡人怎舍得架海金梁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你本是坐朝中开国良将"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "非是臣在金殿告职还乡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老姚期有一本启奏吾王："
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怕的是郭娘娘陷害忠良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "小姚刚打死了太师命丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤离了龙书案把话来讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "君臣们站金阙细谈衷肠："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "那时节孤年幼不能承当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "将孤王赶出都流落他乡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "众举子内其中也有孤王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "又谁知那一箭不曾带伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "科场内怒走了马武子章。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤与那邓先生到卿的宝庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老皇兄曾言道上有高堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "行至在厨房下自尽悬梁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "天下人俱挂孝方称心肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老皇兄，三年孝改三月，三月孝改三日，三日孝改三时，三年、三月、三日、"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "三时，三刻不满，扶保孤王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤念你秉忠心扶保家邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤念你每年间，东挡西除，马不停蹄，血战疆场，到如今你还是扶保孤王！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤念你只剩下一子姚刚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
